<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>PDFUnicorn - pricing plans</title>
	%= include 'site/head'
	%= include 'mixpanel'
  
    <!-- record main page view -->
  	<script type="text/javascript">mixpanel.track('view-pricing-page')</script>
</head>

<body>
	%= include 'site/header'
	
	<style>
	.pdfu-plan {
		margin: 20px;
		
		margin-left: 0;
		margin-right: 0;
		background-color: #fff;
		border-width: 1px;
		border-color: #ddd;
		border-radius: 10px;
		box-shadow: none;
		
		padding: 2px 0 16px 0;
	}
	</style>

    <div class="container">

	  <div class="jumbotron clearfix">
        <h2 style="text-align: center">Generate PDF documents free for 14 days on the Small plan</h2>
        <h3 style="text-align: center">No credit card required</h3>
        <h3 style="text-align: center">Choose a plan to suit your needs any time</h3>
        <div style="text-align: center">
        	<button class="btn btn-primary">Click here to start your free trial now</button>
       	</div>
        <div class="col-sm-3">
        <div class="pdfu-plan">
        	<h3 style="text-align: center">Small</h3>
        	<h2 style="text-align: center">$19/month</h2>
        	<div style="text-align: center">500 units/month</div>
      	</div>
      	</div>
        <div class="col-sm-3">
        <div class="pdfu-plan">
        	<h3 style="text-align: center">Medium</h3>
        	<h2 style="text-align: center">$49/month</h2>
        	<div style="text-align: center">1,500 units/month</div>
      	</div>
      	</div>
        <div class="col-sm-3">
        <div class="pdfu-plan">
        	<h3 style="text-align: center">Large</h3>
        	<h2 style="text-align: center">$99/month</h2>
        	<div style="text-align: center">5,000 units/month</div>
      	</div>
      	</div>
        <div class="col-sm-3">
        <div class="pdfu-plan">
        	<h3 style="text-align: center">X-Large</h3>
        	<h2 style="text-align: center">$199/month</h2>
        	<div style="text-align: center">20,000 units/month</div>
      	</div>
      	</div>
	    <h4 class="text-success" style="text-align: center; margin: 40px 0 0 0">a unit in this context is a page of a pdf or an image in a page</h4>
      </div>
        <div class="text-muted col-sm-offset-3 col-sm-6">
      ok, so the plan names aren't great but they're so relative to what you
      want to do I couldn't come up with any better. If you're creating lower
      value invoices then Small could be "Small Business" but if your invoices
      are enterprise level then Small could be "Enterprise".. you could want to
      create packing slips for DVDs or personalised "how to care for your Ferrari"
      user manuals.  
      	</div>
    </div>

    <script src="/lib/jquery/jquery.js"></script>
    <script src="/lib/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
